overview.en: CTE is a mobile intelligent device-based terminal,integrated blockchain,big data,cloud computing,NFC,GPS and other technologies based on the Ethereum promoters,providing consumers with a more convenient service system and providing more for the development of the physical industry economy,More financial support.
overview.zh: CTE是一条基于以太坊发起的以移动智能设备为终端, 集成区块链、大数据、云计算、NFC、GPS 等技术,为消费者提供更加便捷的服务体系,为实体产业经济的发展提供更多的金融支持。
